86
00:06:37.188 --> 00:06:40.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（雷鳴）

87
00:06:40.858 --> 00:06:42.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
