全然 反応を示さない

103
00:07:37.081 --> 00:07:38.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
もっと悪いことには―

104
00:07:38.458 --> 00:07:41.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
